-week trial-by-fire that is the NFB's Hothouse for animation filmmakers.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1031,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2009-01-01","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Six: Inside","original_language":"en"},{"id":774127,"adult":false,"title":"Roald & Beatrix: The Tail of the Curious Mouse","video":false,"overview":"Roald & Beatrix, the tail of the curious mouse, a heart-warming Christmas film inspired by the true encounter between a six-year-old Roald Dahl and his idol Beatrix Potter. A magical story of what really can happen when you are brave enough to follow your dreams. Joining Dawn French who plays Beatrix, the cast includes Jessica Hynes, Rob Brydon, Alison Steadman, Nina Sosanya, Bill Bailey and Nick Mohammed.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5072,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qttUiMGevgu4y3E6nG4bxXR2Acr.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-24","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/1SMSDSeOF0PWx0EUWRa5tkEkwsd.jpg","original_title":"Roald & Beatrix: The Tail of the Curious Mouse","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1066938,"adult":false,"title":"Natchan's Little Secret","video":false,"overview":"When three drag queens, Virgin, Moririn, and Zubuko, learn that their mentor and former drag queen, Natchan, has died suddenly, they take it upon themselves to keep the secret of her sexuality from her bereaved family.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.219,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/dkDYzmrotdodevB4MQt40UEzUPj.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-13","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/koqzwvlGRdVoeDtSBBue5zh2DjE.jpg","original_title":"ひみつのなっちゃん。","original_language":"ja"},{"id":470731,"adult":false,"title":"The Apple Tree","video":false,"overview":"When Gabe and Jonathan fall in love in the 1940s, they decide to spend their life together in secret. But when Jonathan unexpectedly passes away years later, Gabe is faced with the fact that many Lesbian, Gay, Bisexual and Transgender elders face when they move into retirement homes...he must return into the closet.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.1403,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/1VUF4alEkHTxs7KxfQj4I0bYMBc.jpg","release_date":"2012-01-15","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/1OGRc1Qo79PzUuvJmfgWLeFJJ3Q.jpg","original_title":"The Apple Tree","original_language":"en"},{"id":1459256,"adult":false,"title":"All at Once","video":false,"overview":"On a journey across Central Park, an introspective high school senior develops unexpected feelings for her charismatic co-valedictorian as they discuss love, family, and their futures.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1254,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/agR17MkooVNSfbdbEH1vS0PboJd.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-08","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/uqTyqeNF9g2A6wYEXWmXqnbxgRi.jpg","original_title":"All at Once","original_language":"en"},{"id":8463,"adult":false,"title":"Torch Song Trilogy","video":false,"overview":"Arnold Beckoff is looking for love and acceptance, but as a gay man working as a female impersonator in 1970s New York City, neither come easily. After a series of heartaches, Arnold believes he has found the love of his life in Alan, and the couple make plans to adopt. But when tragedy strikes, Arnold's life is shaken to its very core, leading to a confrontation with his overbearing mother, who has never approved of her son's lifestyle.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5473,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/uoMiWYfycupTa7PxJ1XUwqnN6gO.jpg","release_date":"1988-12-14","vote_average":7.25,"backdrop_path":"/oDGXonGryIJ38XgPSRC3NfYQ6lg.jpg","original_title":"Torch Song Trilogy","original_language":"en"},{"id":8618,"adult":false,"title":"The History Boys","video":false,"overview":"The story of an unruly class of bright, funny history students at a Yorkshire grammar school in pursuit of an undergraduate place at Oxford or Cambridge. Bounced between their maverick English master, a young and shrewd teacher hired to up their test scores, a grossly out-numbered history teacher, and a headmaster obsessed with results, the boys attempt to pass.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5165,"vote_count":211,"poster_path":"/klybhTU75GUcQbzdVXUhsZgq1EV.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-02","vote_average":6.626,"backdrop_path":"/A159OAi9EAU9v4l3sfMhpMqSK5v.jpg","original_title":"The History Boys","original_language":"en"},{"id":1067395,"adult":false,"title":"Jim","video":false,"overview":"Jim, a gay priest, invites a sex worker over for the night. The encounter changes Jim’s life forever, but not as he expects.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.3816,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/rRaevoRngEBxcUnIOcHXcAfmNel.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-13","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/v2gWERoRMzPO4rYhpj1LpyOZ7RT.jpg","original_title":"Jim","original_language":"en"},{"id":1259163,"adult":false,"title":"Roses","video":false,"overview":"Rosa unexpectedly finds herself spending an evening out alone as her daughter throws an 18th birthday party in their house. Wasting time in her small Cornish town, she spies a woman she has met once before - and is drawn to her.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2137,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/xI8dQgYFTYzEUIuo9G44AEsm0TM.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-12","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/8MVMAGxmzsiu4wG71OLZQQLtMcd.jpg","original_title":"Roses","original_language":"en"},{"id":471074,"adult":false,"title":"Connected","video":false,"overview":"\"Connected\" is a about two lonesome people who find each other via a chance encounter on a subway train. They experience happiness in one another for a brief moment in their lives until circumstances out of their control rip them apart. However their paths may once again intersect down the line.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.3412,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/tZtCpslgwRmRSleZIi0GmoWmaWH.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-08","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/iLo62uzRS1YUDePTfvauOq8kE3R.jpg","original_title":"Connected","original_language":"en"},{"id":8391,"adult":false,"title":"When Night Is Falling","video":false,"overview":"Camille is a professor at a Protestant college and is in a long-term relationship with Martin, a respected minister and fellow professor. When Camille meets Petra, a bold and flamboyant performer in a circus troupe, she is inexplicably drawn. Pursuing Petra, Camille throws her whole conservative life into disarray.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.5971,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/6Ac5GLwJ01uli5mCXqXwquR36Y1.jpg","release_date":"1995-02-01","vote_average":6.261,"backdrop_path":"/5CCPKLWg0YWajQEXWYeY2w5c8qS.jpg","original_title":"When Night Is Falling","original_language":"en"},{"id":8436,"adult":false,"title":"The Page Turner","video":false,"overview":"Mélanie Prouvost, a ten-year-old butcher's daughter, is a gifted pianist. That is why she and her parents decide that she sit for the Conservatory entrance exam. Although Mélanie is very likely to be admitted, she unfortunately gets distracted by the president of the jury's offhand attitude and she fails. Ten years later, Mélanie becomes her page turner, waiting patiently for her revenge.","genre_ids":[18,10402,53],"popularity":0.4351,"vote_count":145,"poster_path":"/lBomGoLZKklJWb5hMvcy44WbUsd.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-09","vote_average":6.521,"backdrop_path":"/uyZMq9VTihrWBVXzIQUkB8P8Nnq.jpg","original_title":"La Tourneuse de pages","original_language":"fr"},{"id":661384,"adult":false,"title":"The Pier Man","video":false,"overview":"Theo is a young docker languishing in his native port. His life flows at the monotonous rhythm of cargo ships passing by. Through his encounter with Giuseppe, a disillusioned sailor ashore for a while, Theo will gather the courage to face the waves to escape his dull existence by trying to get into Giuseppe's gruff crew.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1416,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/sC84npT8wSF1Nr9TE6x3R2eS1Ai.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-07","vote_average":1.8,"backdrop_path":"/x2fPXY8kkTjdki9yZsYtpA8vmmz.jpg","original_title":"L'homme jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1067485,"adult":false,"title":"Sebastian","video":false,"overview":"Max is a 25-year-old freelance writer and aspiring novelist who seems well on his way to success in London’s cultural spheres. Yet by night, he finds a different kind of exhilaration as a sex worker with the pseudonym Sebastian, meeting men via an escorting platform. Max uses his experiences as Sebastian to fuel his stories and the worthy debut novel that he has been longing to write, finally seems within reach.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2755,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/22JTGme2MLETmvhHQdiKP78S5Qf.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-02","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/kEvBFfqCtJvtvwZcrprAT3dSvij.jpg","original_title":"Sebastian","original_language":"en"},{"id":470901,"adult":false,"title":"Face 2 Face","video":false,"overview":"Over a series of video chats, a teenage outcast reaches out to his childhood friend, but finds that behind the veneer of popularity and a seemingly perfect life, she hides a disturbing secret.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3045,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/lciZWx3qVPUxGnw9rzNBqNgQPuN.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/9VoU9AV6POqPSVXVR832BZDBAr.jpg","original_title":"Face 2 Face","original_language":"en"},{"id":1459233,"adult":false,"title":"Violet","video":false,"overview":"Amid the colorful Panagbenga Festival, a young woman embarks on a journey of self-discovery, navigating first love, desire, and the awakening of her sexuality. Through passion and innocence, she learns how love and intimacy shape her path to adulthood.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":2.5985,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/u9McUubbCryR9l2816AIYGPICpn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-15","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Violet","original_language":"tl"},{"id":861043,"adult":false,"title":"Boys Night","video":false,"overview":"Bouncing around from genre to genre, this stellar collection of 6 short films from Mattioli Productions showcases some of the most cutting edge recent gay cinema from the United States and Australia. Sit back, relax and get ready to make it a BOYS NIGHT.\r The short films are: Hopelessly (2018); Innocent Boy (2020); Mass (2020); Miles (2017); Sacrifice (2018); Tooth 4 Tooth (2020).","genre_ids":[18,27],"popularity":1.9605,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/mBFWk5uR9Tq2xrEy4VcbsBLyZ9H.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-07","vote_average":2.333,"backdrop_path":"/2IbO0cef2rRJDO26ODnxxc8eZd5.jpg","original_title":"Boys Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":471156,"adult":false,"title":"In the Name of the Father","video":false,"overview":"The short film depicts the life of a boy who is constantly sexually abused by his father. Leonardo Miggiorin brilliantly plays the role of this boy, who belongs to a poor and unstructured family.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2324,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/rNqUVdZ64HuFxUe9TwUYwCNfQob.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-01","vote_average":4.773,"backdrop_path":"/7nWEZ0nM99WjycLP5v44IpfeUgs.jpg","original_title":"Em Nome do Pai","original_language":"pt"},{"id":471159,"adult":false,"title":"Sergeant Garcia","video":false,"overview":"Based on a story by the same name by Caio Fernando Abreu, it tells the encounter of a young man and a sergeant in the 1970s.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.3333,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/5m0bHWZojZGuclhFmmC5gnQS8BJ.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-02","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":"/kDhxu9C5prfnWZD0qIPFDBFlVzZ.jpg","original_title":"Sargento Garcia","original_language":"pt"},{"id":8952,"adult":false,"title":"I Love You Phillip Morris","video":false,"overview":"Steven Russell leads a seemingly average life – an organ player in the local church, happily married to Debbie, and a member of the local police force. That is until he has a severe car accident that leads him to the ultimate epiphany: he’s gay and he’s going to live life to the fullest – even if he has to break the law to do it. Taking on an extravagant lifestyle, Steven turns to cons and fraud to make ends meet and is eventually sent to the State Penitentiary where he meets the love of his life, a sensitive, soft-spoken man named Phillip Morris. His devotion to freeing Phillip from jail and building the perfect life together prompts him to attempt (and often succeed at) one impossible con after another.","genre_ids":[35,80,18,10749],"popularity":2.1673,"vote_count":1780,"poster_path":"/qtAuWLGQ7N4PNQ6boZeqqoUY2l9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-04","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/sGelj98GTvGgx9yq2vNdvRoyXH4.jpg","original_title":"I Love You Phillip Morris","original_language":"en"},{"id":277695,"adult":false,"title":"The Boys of Cellblock Q","video":false,"overview":"The Boys of Cellblock Q is set within the bowels of the Sunnyvale Labor Farm. Without the presence of women, the prisoners indulge in regular trysts with one another, make full use out of the jail's supply of priests, turn the eyes several policemen, and help a young convict learn the ins and outs of the prison community.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.1262,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/6GWiVMbmM6y3o5H87lc78vgxaLx.jpg","release_date":"1992-07-01","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Boys of Cellblock Q","original_language":"en"},{"id":661925,"adult":false,"title":"Softie","video":false,"overview":"Ten-year-old Johnny stands out from his family and his tough neighborhood in Eastern France. He's sensitive, intelligent and interested in all kinds of things way beyond his years. With curiosity, he observes the ups and downs of his young single mother's turbulent love life. Things change when a new teacher, fresh from the big city, takes over Johnny's class. Mr. Adamski believes in Johnny and wants to open a new world to him. The sophisticated young teacher also intrigues the boy.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.8209,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/kwj7twCx2fAYdoslqzJv1rHQdlK.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/18pvm5koeoCZNw8aPEY4jcMUGFn.jpg","original_title":"Petite nature","original_language":"fr"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt30524053","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148589,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"PH","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"tl","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-01-05T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"R-18"}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"original_network":null,"screenwriters":null,"based_on":null,"filming_location":null,"narrative_location":null,"review_score_rt":null,"review_score_mc":null,"box_office":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"collection_id":null,"wikidata_metadata":{},"mood_tags":null,"trope_tags":null,"vibe_description":null,"ai_enriched_at":null,"ai_enrichment_version":0}}]]
